name: Unidentified_Anchorhead_attendant
content:
A Human female worked as an attendant at the spaceport in Anchorhead on the desert planet Tatooine during the reign of the Galactic Empire. She was checking passengers departing Anchorhead in 9 BBY when Jedi-in-exile Obi-Wan Kenobi departed for Daiyu to rescue Princess Leia Organa, who had been kidnapped by mercenaries.
The attendant first appeared in "Part I" of the Disney+ live action television series Obi Wan Kenobi, directed by Deborah Chow and released on May 26, 2022. She was played by Sonia Jackson and credited as "Attendant."
